302419-PIQUA WWTP 005 OUTFALL OUTFALL TO GREAT MIAMI R.
MonitoringLocationDescriptionText: Piqua historically maintained two final effluent outfalls (001 and 005) to the GMR. Outfall 005 discharged in the dam pool immediately upstream of the Piqua Power dam at RM 114.29 (East Bank). Outfall 001 is located at RM 114.06 downstream of the dam. Operators had the option of discharging to either location. Historical operating data indicate that the plant discharged solely through Outfall 005 since 1995 to help cool the power plant dam pool. The discharge from the power plant was eliminated by 2005. Deterioration of outfall 005 resulted in the eventual closure and elimination of the discharge point in 2010. Piqua now discharges solely through Outfall 001 (RM 114.06)

H02W10-PIQUA WWTP 001 OUTFALL OUTFALL TO GREAT MIAMI R.
MonitoringLocationDescriptionText:
Piqua historically maintained two final effluent outfalls (001 and 005) to the GMR. Outfall 005 discharged in the dam pool immediately upstream of the Piqua Power dam at RM 114.29 (East Bank). Outfall 001 is located at RM 114.06 downstream of the dam. Operators had the option of discharging to either location. Historical operating data indicate that the plant discharged solely through Outfall 005 since 1995 to help cool the power plant dam pool. The
discharge from the power plant was eliminated by 2005. Deterioration of outfall 005 resulted in the eventual closure and elimination of the discharge point in 2010. Piqua now discharges solely through Outfall 001 (RM 114.06)
